-- Saudi Ceramics Second-Quarter Profit Rises 11% to $15.4 Million on Output
-- Glen Carey
-- 2010-07-11T05:55:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-11/saudi-ceramics-second-quarter-profit-rises-11-to-15-4-million-on-output.html

          
          
             Saudi Ceramic Co. posted an 11
percent increase in second-quarter profit to 57.9 million riyals
($15.4 million) from 52.1 million riyals in the year-earlier
period on higher sales and increased output, the company said
today on the Saudi bourse website.  
